h1.  ==   A simple blog with Ruby on Rails       ==

p.    This application is a simple blog. It is developed using ruby on rails framework.
      The features this blog consists of:
         1 Posting article into the blog by the owner
         2 Blogers are able to post comments on these articles
         3 User authentication
         4 Restrictions for unauthenticated blogers
         
         

      I hope this application would help beginners like me in a way or another
   
   
